latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Monotonous Boring Lipstick 💄? ⠀
⠀
Convert any lipstick into a metallic finish⠀
Don't run out and buy a new lipstick, just apply some highlighter or eyeshadow on top of any lipstick to give it a gorgeous metallic finish. ⠀
